==Inventory==
*[[Special attack]] weapon, such as [[Burning claws]]
*1-2 [[Super combat potion]]s
*4-6 [[Prayer potion]]s or [[super restore]]s
*Teleport such as [[Xeric's talisman]], [[Teleport to house (tablet)|House tablets]], or [[Book of the dead]] to reach the Forthos Dungeon
*Slash weapon to cut through webs, such as a [[Wilderness sword 1]], unless wearing the aranea boots.
*[[Teleport to house (tablet)|House tablets]] or [[Ring of dueling]] for a one click teleport, stat restoration and access to a bank
*[[Book of the dead]] for casting resurrection spells on the [[Arceuus spellbook]]
*[[Rune pouch]] with runes for [[Resurrect Greater Ghost]]
*The rest [[Cooked karambwan]]s or better

Optionally:
*[[Ring of stone]] or other one-click [[transformation rings]] to unfreeze from Sarachnis' web attack
*[[Death runes]] and [[Soul runes]] for [[Death Charge]] for more special attacks



'''Note:''' Players using [[Aranea boots]] do not need to bring a slash weapon for webs, and do not benefit from using a [[transformation ring]]

