Magic (Tumeken's shadow) = [[Tumeken's shadow]]'s high accuracy and damage make it uniquely effective against Sarachnis when used with high-level magic equipment, although poor special attack weapons and lower melee defence lead to melee setups generally performing better overall.

While using [[Protect from Missiles]] and standing by the [[empty sarcophagus]] at the eastern side of the lair, the player will occasionally be out of the melee spawns' aggression range and outside of Sarachnis' melee range, and able to reach Sarachnis no matter where she is, negating the need for [[aranea boots]].

